Ethyl Corp said its subsidiariescompleted the acquisiton of Nelson Research and Development Co&lt;NELR>.    The merger was approved following completion on Jan 27 of atender offer valued at approximately 55 mln dlrs, the companysaid.    It added that Nelson, based in Irvine, Calif., will beoperated as a wholly-owned subsidiary of Ethyl.    Nelson designs and develops new drugs, Ethyl said. Reuter&#3;